&lt;p&gt;Python语言支持以下类型的运算符:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://www.runoob.com/python/python-operators.html#ysf1&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;算术运算符&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://www.runoob.com/python/python-operators.html#ysf2&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
